If you have watched lost, we all know these numbers are of important value:

4 8 15 16 23 42

Lets try to use our luck to get these numbers. Lets see who's destiny will be to open a hatch, survive a plane crash, meet John Locke, or even see the future...

Instructions: The idea is to get the numbers as seen above, and in the TV series LOST, using Dice rolls and trying to roll those series of numbers. For maximum effectiveness, use these specific dice in this order:

4 sided die, 8 sided die, 20 sided die, 20 sided die, 100 sided die, 100 sided die

I suppose another rule would be to not post twice in a row. Lets get this started!
